---
title: "Colossus: The Forbin Project"
format: "film"
category: "c"
yearReleased: "1969"
author: "Joseph Sargent"
---
Colossus, a US supercomputer designed to put an end to war, gangs up with its Soviet counterpart, Guardian, to form a monolithic totalitarian machine that ends war at the price of also ending all human freedom.
 
Recommended for inclusion in the new <a href="https://anarchysf.com/">anarchySF</a> website by <em>Fifth Estate</em>, in its Spring 2019 edition.
